"If a police officer ever pulls you over for speeding and asks, &amp;quot;Do you know how fast you were going?&amp;quot; an insightful, though perhaps unwise, reply would be, ""Relative to what?"""
And then, as you sit in the backseat of the police car and feel it accelerate toward jail, you can add, &amp;quot;But some things are absolute!&amp;quot;
So I'm an artist, but a little bit of a peculiar one.
